dialogueLines.text: "What a beautiful sunny sky..." you think. (Click Next to continue)
"...The perfect day to make some deliveries."
You see a duckling to the North. Maybe he has a letter for you to deliver!
Use the WASD keys to move around. Head North (up) to talk to the duckling.
Press E to talk to the duckling
DIDDLY THE DUCKLING: "Hello mister! Can you help me?"
"Can you deliver this card to my friend across the river?"
"Outer duckspace"
"Oh, ok... It's just that I'm never gonna see her again..."
*Sniff sniff* "I just wanted to say goodbye to her..."
"Thank you! I would fly across but I don't have big strong wings like you!"

options.text: You could also swim across, you know.

dialogueLines.text: "Just look for the purple bear across the river!"

...but my mom told me not to leave the nest while she's visiting outer duckspace. Why do your parents want you to move again?
Because there's more fish on the other side? What a load of quack. As soon as I get better at swimming I will come visit! Your best friend, Diddly.
